column5: ? https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YFa4uyGdmA0&t=47s  Broke back laker and a nice clean one.
Hey Brian, that's a great set up you have . Can't get any closer to the water. Nice lakers also. How do you deal with those speed boats darting on the water?? ??

Thanks  There was a bass tourny on. . They were out sat and sun. I have my net way up in the air. Hope they see it. ?  I found it funny that all the boats went to the  east side. Guess there are no bass on the west side. LOL
Nice fish Brian. Saw the title and figured you were either a cowboy or caught a cuddlefish ?

Brian I was leery to open this thread. If I  read Broke Back anything I think of the movie Brokeback Mountain Ever seen it? you should. Great video though, you sure have a Pro set up there. Way to go Go Pro. Have you ever heard the saying?  "You have a face for radio."
I wonder if the Johnstons fished the west side ? Thats a big time bass tourney, big money, big names, and here you are out catching mutated greasers lol The loony tooner strikes again!
